RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT 'ALL' BRNCODE,'ANY BRANCH' BRNDESC FROM DUAL UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE BRNCODE,BRANCH_NAME BRNDESC FROM STTM_CORE_BRANCH WHERE ONCE_AUTH='Y' AND RECORD_STAT='O'

SELECT 'ALL' EXTSYSTEM ,'ANY EXTERNAL SYSTEM' EXTSYSDESC FROM DUAL UNION SELECT SOURCE_CODE EXTSYSTEM ,SOURCE_DESC EXTSYSDESC FROM COTM_SOURCE WHERE NVL(AUTH_STAT,'U') = 'A' AND NVL(RECORD_STAT,'C') = 'O'
SELECT A.TRN_CODE OFSTXNCODE , A.TRN_DESC OFSTXNCODEDESC FROM STTMS_TRN_CODE A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O'AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY A.TRN_CODE
SELECT DISTINCT AMOUNT_TAG OFSAMTTAG ,DESCRIPTION OFSAMTTAGDESC FROM CSTB_AMOUNT_TAG ORDER BY AMOUNT_TAG
